sections.Biography:
===Background===
Maekar was a King in the [[House Targaryen|Targaryen dynasty]]. He was the father of [[Aerion Targaryen|Aerion]], who killed himself drinking [[wildfire]]; [[Aemon]], who would become a [[Maester]] in [[Castle Black]]; and [[Aegon V Targaryen]], who would succeed him on the [[Iron Throne]].&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Baelor]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

===[[Season 1]]===
When revealing [[Jon Snow]] his true identity and origins, Maester Aemon mentions the name of his father.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Baelor]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
